{"id": "1193061253673926676", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "type": 0, "author_id": "564327990398287904", "author_name": "momoshiocha", "author_bot": false, "content": "想問一下今天那個莉莉的盾是什麼邏輯", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T05:19:28.882000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193061332124172348", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "type": 0, "author_id": "564327990398287904", "author_name": "momoshiocha", "author_bot": false, "content": "每回合長一個出來嗎？", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T05:19:47.586000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193061373798797312", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "type": 0, "author_id": "564327990398287904", "author_name": "momoshiocha", "author_bot": false, "content": "好硬敲不動😭", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T05:19:57.522000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193067429023207518", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "type": 19, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "莉莉的被動【不滅之花】初始會有一個倒數，\n每受到1點傷害都會降低，當降至0以下時，\n她會直接改變當前的行動意圖，\n在下次行動生成一個基於最大生命的護盾（記得是15%）\n\n如果護盾沒有被打破，她會用殘餘盾量的兩倍恢復血量\n\n這個被動並不是永久存在的，比方說在恢復血量的那回合，\n她會使用【粘泥彙集】來重新獲得【不滅之花】這個被動，\n該回合所承受的所有傷害，\n既不會被護盾抵擋，也不會降低【不滅之花】的倒數，算是比較好的進攻時機", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T05:44:01.200000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-06T05:53:00.494000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["564327990398287904"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193061253673926676", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193067666664079441", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "type": 19, "author_id": "564327990398287904", "author_name": "momoshiocha", "author_bot": false, "content": "原來如此！所以要控制出牌時間敲暈莉莉！", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T05:44:57.858000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["190674373483429888"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1193067429023207518", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193068016439664752", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "我是玩超維，把超維空間的時間拉在那附近來輸出，\n或者也可以用奧吉爾之類的穿刺來對護盾造成可觀傷害，\n穿刺會同時削減護盾跟本體血量，可以讓她不要回那麼多", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T05:46:21.251000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1193068095133204622", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "火力不夠打太高難度，有時候真的會變成死循環......", "timestamp": "2024-01-06T05:46:40.013000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
